videos.description: Punter Cole Moos keeps the snap and runs for the first down to extend the Kansas drive.
videos.headline: Kansas fakes punt for first down

videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer finds Mims for 56-yard gain

videos.description: Charlie Brewer finds Jordan Feuerbacher for the 25-yard touchdown to give the Bears a 14-3 lead.
videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer tosses a 25-yard pass to Feuerbacher for TD

videos.description: Gavin Holmes runs it in for the 4-yard touchdown to extend Baylor's lead to 21-6.
videos.headline: Baylor's Holmes rushes for 4-yard TD

videos.description: Baylor's Rajah Preciado strips the ball loose and it is recovered by Baylor's James Lynch.

videos.headline: Kansas' Herbert finds the edge for 43-yard gain

videos.description: Terence Williams plunges into the end zone on 4th and goal to extend Baylor's lead  to 28-9.
videos.headline: Baylor's Williams barrels in for 1-yard TD

videos.description: Baylor's Harrison Hand stretches out to make the interception in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Baylor's Hand comes up with key interception.

videos.description: Charlie Brewer lobs it up to Ishmail Wainright for the 9-yard touchdown giving Brewer three touchdown passes in his first career start.
videos.headline: Baylor freshman Brewer gets third TD pass of the day
